    Ensure that RestResultSetReceiver.setNext throws an error
    
    Callers must handle thrown exceptions.
    
    Fixes a regression introduced in 9b61be3
    
    (cherry picked from commit bd3219ec49ccabf5a70191a20fba2cadd07ed6ac)
    
    # Conflicts:
    #       docs/appendices/release-notes/5.10.9.rst

